data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER! SELLING HOME TURNKEY. Don't miss out on this amazing opportunity to own a beautiful home that is sure to go quickly. Situated in a secure gated community, Lake Ashton, this home offers the added benefit of resort style amenities and activities. The Sebastian model boasts exquisite tile plank flooring in select rooms, complemented by high ceilings for an elegant touch. The kitchen is equipped with breakfast bar, stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and stylish cabinetry. The dinette area with double windows overlooks the screened lanai.  The living room with tray ceiling is warm and inviting. Stackable triple sliders separate the LR and the Lanai. This seasonally occupied  home shows like a brand new home. Bring your creativity and make it your own. Bedroom 2 and 3 are conveniently located to the guest bathroom and a linen closet is available for your storage needs. The master suite is the perfect place to retreat in the evening. The ensuite bathroom offers comfort height His/Her vanities, large walk in shower with glass block window and separate water closet. A window was added to the water closet for additional light. The lanai with bump out birdcage has slate flooring and overlooks the golf course. The washer/dryer will convey and the laundry room has plumbing for a wash tub to be installed. The Florida lifestyle of your dreams awaits you here, and with a competitive price, this home is an incredible value. Don't wait too long; schedule a showing to see this remarkable home for yourself before it's gone! Furniture is available and negotiable. Lake Ashton offers 2 private 18- Hole golf courses. Golf memberships are optional. Residents also enjoy a large Clubhouse with outdoor resort style pool, Charm City (Restaurant), Bowling lanes, media center, fitness center, Bocce Courts, Tennis and Racquetball courts, movie theater and grand ballroom. Also located in Lake Ashton is a Health and Fitness Center that features an indoor lap pool, pickle ball courts, fitness center, craft and card rooms, and MORE.
